<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 06:19:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着贸易争端升级，欧盟各国政府对中国电动汽车关税犹豫不决</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-governments-waver-over-chinese-ev-tariffs-trade-spat-escalates-2024-07-03/</link><description>欧盟国家在是否支持对中国制造的电动汽车征收额外关税的问题上犹豫不决，突显出布鲁塞尔在为其最大贸易案争取支持方面面临的挑战，而北京则威胁要进行大范围的报复。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 06:04:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-governments-waver-over-chinese-ev-tariffs-trade-spat-escalates-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，欧盟拟对中国特木和希因征收进口关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/eu-takes-aim-chinas-temu-shein-with-proposed-import-duty-ft-reports-2024-07-03/</link><description>英国《金融时报》周三援引三名知情人士的话报道称，欧盟正在制定计划，对从 Temu、Shein 和 AliExpress 等中国在线零售商购买的廉价商品征收关税。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 04:19:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/eu-takes-aim-chinas-temu-shein-with-proposed-import-duty-ft-reports-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示中国服务业活动增速创8个月新低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-services-activity-growth-hits-8-month-low-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-07-03/</link><description>周三的一项私营部门调查显示，受新订单增长放缓拖累，中国服务业活动增速为八个月来最慢，六月份信心跌至四年低点，这表明需要更多经济刺激措施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 01:50:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-services-activity-growth-hits-8-month-low-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>普京抵达哈萨克斯坦出席中俄主导的上合组织峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-arrives-kazakhstan-russia-china-dominated-sco-summit-2024-07-03/</link><description>克里姆林宫表示，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京周三抵达哈萨克斯坦，参加地区安全和防务会谈，以及一系列双边会议，包括与中国和土耳其领导人的会晤。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 01:31:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-arrives-kazakhstan-russia-china-dominated-sco-summit-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称中国在中国海岸附近扣押渔船</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-china-seizes-fishing-boat-near-chinese-coast-2024-07-02/</link><description>台湾海岸警卫队表示，周二晚间，中国官员登上并扣押了一艘在靠近台湾控制岛屿的中国海岸附近作业的台湾渔船，并将其带到中国港口，紧张局势进一步升级。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 22:37:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-china-seizes-fishing-boat-near-chinese-coast-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，埃克森-赫斯仲裁小组即将组建</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/exxon-hess-arbitration-panel-nears-formation-sources-say-2024-07-02/</link><description>两名知情人士告诉路透社，最后一名成员已被选入三人仲裁小组，该小组旨在解决埃克森美孚针对雪佛龙以 530 亿美元收购赫斯公司提出的索赔。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 21:12:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/exxon-hess-arbitration-panel-nears-formation-sources-say-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>意大利扣押运往利比亚的中国制造军用无人机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/italy-seizes-chinese-made-military-drones-destined-libya-2024-07-02/</link><description>意大利海关警察和海关机构周二表示，意大利当局拦截并扣押了两架中国制造的军用无人机，它们的目的地是利比亚，伪装成风力涡轮机设备。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:33:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/italy-seizes-chinese-made-military-drones-destined-libya-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>智库称，美国军事基地附近的新古巴雷达站可能有助于中国间谍活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/new-cuban-radar-site-near-us-military-base-could-aid-china-spying-think-tank-2024-07-02/</link><description>古巴正在建设一个新的雷达站，可能能够监视美国附近的​​关塔那摩湾海军基地，这是华盛顿智库利用卫星图像发现的，这是该国监视能力的最新升级，长期以来一直被认为与中国有关。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:32:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/new-cuban-radar-site-near-us-military-base-could-aid-china-spying-think-tank-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，柏林将阻止曼恩能源解决方案公司的燃气轮机部门向中国出售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/berlin-block-sale-man-energy-solutions-gas-turbine-unit-china-sources-say-2024-07-02/</link><description>三名知情人士周二告诉路透社，德国将阻止大众汽车子公司曼能源解决方案公司燃气轮机部门向一家中国公司出售的计划。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 15:45:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/berlin-block-sale-man-energy-solutions-gas-turbine-unit-china-sources-say-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>国土安全部称美国包机驱逐中国移民</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-deported-chinese-migrants-charter-flight-homeland-security-says-2024-07-02/</link><description>美国国土安全部周二表示，美国在周末将试图非法入境的中国人驱逐回中国，这是自 2018 年以来的首次大型包机。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 14:22:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-deported-chinese-migrants-charter-flight-homeland-security-says-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国将六家公司列入贸易限制名单，其中四家用于培训中国军队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-adds-six-companies-trade-restriction-list-four-training-chinas-military-2024-07-02/</link><description>据政府公告称，美国周二将六家公司列入贸易限制名单，其中四家因与中国军队训练有联系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 13:23:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-adds-six-companies-trade-restriction-list-four-training-chinas-military-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>文件显示，拜登2024年吊销了中国华为的8张许可证</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/biden-revoked-8-licenses-chinas-huawei-2024-document-shows-2024-07-02/</link><description>据路透社最先报道的一份文件显示，拜登政府今年吊销了八项允许一些公司向中国电信设备巨头华为运送货物的许可证，试图向这家复兴的公司施压。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 12:06:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/biden-revoked-8-licenses-chinas-huawei-2024-document-shows-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪与法国艾文斯建立欧洲合作伙伴关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-forms-european-partnership-with-frances-ayvens-2024-07-02/</link><description>法国兴业银行的汽车租赁部门艾文斯与中国电动汽车公司比亚迪周二宣布建立欧洲市场合作伙伴关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 12:01:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-forms-european-partnership-with-frances-ayvens-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾将“坚持不懈”保护南海利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-says-be-relentless-protecting-interests-south-china-sea-2024-07-02/</link><description>菲律宾和中国周二一致认为，需要“恢复信任”和“重建信心”，以更好地管理海上争端，尽管马尼拉告诉其邻国，它将“毫不留情”地保护其在南海的利益。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 11:06:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-says-be-relentless-protecting-interests-south-china-sea-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>被控为中国从事间谍活动的挪威男子出庭</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/norwegian-citizen-arrested-alleged-spying-china-ntb-agency-reports-2024-07-02/</link><description>一名警方官员表示，一名挪威男子周二在奥斯陆法院出庭，面临代表中国从事间谍活动的指控，最初将被拘留四个星期，这是最新一起涉嫌中国在欧洲从事间谍活动的案件。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 09:35:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/norwegian-citizen-arrested-alleged-spying-china-ntb-agency-reports-2024-07-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>